title: fanoutqa: What is the area in square kilometers of the city that hosts the alma mater of all partners of the main actors from 'How I Met Your Mother' who eventually hosted the Academy Awards? (498337828f5896d3)

chat_history.content: What is the area in square kilometers of the city that hosts the alma mater of all partners of the main actors from 'How I Met Your Mother' who eventually hosted the Academy Awards?

I'm going to assume you want to know the area of the city that hosts the alma mater of all partners of the main actors from 'How I Met Your Mother', who have also hosted the Academy Awards.

The main actors from 'How I Met Your Mother' are Neil Patrick Harris, Cobie Smulders, Josh Radnor, Alyson Hannigan, and Jason Segel.

Neil Patrick Harris is married to David Burtka, who attended the University of Michigan, located in Ann Arbor, Michigan. According to a 2019 publication, Ann Arbor has an area of 27.9 square miles (72.249 km²).

Cobie Smulders is married to Taran Killam, who attended the University of California, Los Angeles (UCLA) in Los Angeles, California. The area of Los Angeles is 1,214.9 km².

Alyson Hannigan's husband Alexis Denisof attended the State University of New York at Purchase, located in Purchase, New York, which has an area of 8.404 km².

Jason Segel's wife, Alexis Mixter, studied at New York University, located in New York City, which has an area of 302.64 mi² (783.81 km²).

Josh Radnor's wife, Julia Maurer, went to Northwestern University, located in Evanston, Illinois. The total area of Evanston is 7.82 mi² (20.254 km²).

The area in square kilometres of the city that hosts the alma mater of all partners of the main actors from 'How I Met Your Mother' who eventually hosted the Academy Awards is 2,223.813 km².
